Materials... *yawns*{短暂停}
Did I buy them?{短暂停}
Oh, I seem to have forgotten something. Let's talk next time.

...(drowsy) Oh, chatting.{短暂停}
Back then, at this hour,{短暂停}
even on clear, beautiful days,{短暂停}it was hard to get me to talk.

About what to chat about... (thinking)
Oh, {短暂停}
Tonight's sky.

...(drowsy) I didn't want to come out, {短暂停}
but the weather is so nice, {短暂停}
perfect for gathering materials.
